name: Franklin Growth ETF Portfolio
longDescription: The fund investing in a diversified mix of exchange traded funds (ETFs) that invest in Canadian, U.S. and international fixed income and equity securities. The fund provide longterm capital appreciation with additional stability derived from investing in income.
